{"tid":1642400,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣核彈]黑警既威水史比人用時間軸去公開記錄","createTime":"2019-10-09T16:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T19:06:33.000Z","uid":258866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfbe468a9dae80891644eafdca8d219b8ea6851","tid":1642400,"uid":258866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"黑警咁多片同埋威水史 梗係要好似MARVEL 咁整條時間線 中文連英文咁清清楚楚比人知啦<br />\n等左咁多個月, D相呀文章呀片呀 愈黎愈多, 全能既連登仔都未有所舉動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 再唔整就整唔切架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且香港人咁善忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全能既連登仔可摸耳整個timeline網頁/app 等香港人記得D黑警做過幾多威水野<br />\n<br />\n利申係電腦白痴, 其他幫到手既可以幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好整左個範本/雲端 有個範本之後大家可以幫手更新<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">ideas are bulletproof</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡簡單單, 暫時搵到呢款<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aveego.com/userfiles/image/timeline_horizontal.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aveego.com%2Fuserfiles%2Fimage%2Ftimeline_horizontal.png&h=98cf844f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aveego.com/userfiles/image/timeline_vertical.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aveego.com%2Fuserfiles%2Fimage%2Ftimeline_vertical.png&h=38a84fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\njQuery Timelinr<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aveego.com/html/o_37244_0_/jquery%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6-%E8%B6%95%E4%B8%8A%E6%BD%AE%E6%B5%81%E7%8E%A9timeline.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aveego.com%2Fhtm